(HIGH-LEVEL ARCHITECTURE) Tj
T*
(? Client Layer: React SPA renders pages for pets, shop, cart, user dashboard, staff/admin) Tj
T*
(dashboards.) Tj
T*
(? API Layer: Express routes grouped by domain \(`/api/auth`, `/api/pets`, `/api/adoptions`,) Tj
T*
(etc.\).) Tj
T*
(? Security Layer: Bearer token middleware validates JWT and injects user claims.) Tj
T*
(? Data Layer: SQLite relational tables for profiles, pets, adoptions, products, cart items,) Tj
T*
(orders, order items, medical records, notifications.) Tj
T*
(? Integration Layer: Razorpay payment services.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(DATABASE ENTITIES \(MAJOR TABLES\)) Tj
T*
(? `profiles`) Tj
T*
(? `pets`) Tj
T*
(? `adoptions`) Tj
T*
(? `products`) Tj
T*
(? `cart_items`) Tj
T*
(? `orders`) Tj
T*
(? `order_items`) Tj
T*
(? `medical_records`) Tj
T*
(? `notifications`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(NON-FUNCTIONAL ENGINEERING CHARACTERISTICS) Tj
T*
(? Modularity: clear separation between frontend API client and backend route handlers.) Tj
T*
(? Maintainability: TypeScript typing for domain entities and API contracts.) Tj
T*
(? Security basics: hashed passwords and protected routes.) Tj
T*
(? Scalability baseline: role-driven workflows and normalized relational entities.) Tj
T*
(? Deployability: Dockerfile-based build/start process.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(BUILD AND EXECUTION FLOW \(CURRENT PROJECT\)) Tj
T*
(1. Install dependencies with `npm install`.) Tj
T*
(2. Configure environment variables \(`GEMINI_API_KEY`, optional `DATABASE_PATH`\).) Tj
T*
(3. Start server via `npm run dev` \(tsx executes backend\).) Tj
T*
(4. Build frontend via `npm run build`.) Tj
T*
(5. Run production container using Dockerfile \(`npm start`\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(TOOLS AND DEPENDENCIES SNAPSHOT) Tj
T*
(? Runtime/Frameworks: Node.js, Express, React, Vite) Tj
T*
(? Security: bcryptjs, jsonwebtoken) Tj
T*
(? Database: better-sqlite3) Tj
T*
(? UI/UX: Tailwind CSS, lucide-react, motion, sonner) Tj
T*
(? Build/Dev: TypeScript, tsx, autoprefixer) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(LIMITATIONS \(CURRENT STATE\)) Tj
T*
(? Hardcoded JWT secret and Razorpay test credentials should be moved fully to environment) Tj
T*
(variables.) Tj
T*
(? SQLite is ideal for mini projects but not horizontally scalable for high concurrency.) Tj
T*
(? No automated test suite is currently configured.) Tj
T*
(? Some API and UI error-handling paths can be further hardened.) Tj
T*
() Tj
